---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions - Imperial Picks" description="Read the Terms and Conditions for Imperial Picks (https://imperialpicks.in). Learn about website usage guidelines, intellectual property clauses, liability limits, and legal compliance.">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="relative bg-slate-50 min-h-screen">
    <!-- Background Patterns -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern pointer-events-none"></div>
    
    <!-- Header Hero -->
    <section class="relative pt-16 pb-10 sm:pt-20 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
          Terms & Conditions
        </h1>
        <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
          <span>Website URL: <a href="https://imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">https://imperialpicks.in</a></span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline text-slate-300">•</span>
          <span>Last Updated: June 10, 2026</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Terms Content -->
    <section class="relative py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-xs space-y-8">
          
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Welcome to Imperial Picks. These Terms & Conditions govern your access to and use of our directory and online calculators located at <a href="https://imperialpicks.in" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">https://imperialpicks.in</a>. By browsing or using this website, you agree to comply with and be bound by these terms. If you disagree with any part of these terms, please stop using the website.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 1 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              1. Acceptance of Terms
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Your use of this platform constitutes a legally binding agreement to follow these website usage rules. We reserves the right to modify or replace these terms at any time without prior notification. Continued use of the website following changes indicates your explicit approval.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 2 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              2. Intellectual Property Rights
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Unless otherwise stated, all material on Imperial Picks—including our editorial reviews, comparison analyses, custom graphic assets, interactive calculator code designs, and website layouts—is the exclusive intellectual property of Imperial Picks. You may access the content for personal, non-commercial use only. You must not copy, reprint, reproduce, distribute, or exploit our materials without prior written authorization.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 3 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              3. Acceptable Use
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              You agree to use Imperial Picks only for lawful purposes. Prohibited actions include:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <li>
                Using scrapers, crawlers, or automated harvesting scripts to copy our tool databases or copy blogs.
              </li>
              <li>
                Using automated script bots or click farms to inflate upvotes or submit fake product votes.
              </li>
              <li>
                Injecting malicious code, spam links, or performing Denial of Service (DoS) attacks on our servers.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 4 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              4. Limitation of Liability
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Imperial Picks operates as an educational and informational directory catalog.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <li>
                <strong>Calculators:</strong> Our marketing, SaaS, and financial calculators estimate projections based on mathematical averages. They do not constitute financial commitments or professional advice. We assume no liability for campaign losses, pricing miscalculations, or ad spend damages.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Tool Performance:</strong> We represent third-party software as accurately as possible, but we cannot warrant that the reviewed AI tools or SaaS products are secure, functional, or free of errors. You interact with third-party software at your own discretion.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 5 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              5. Content Accuracy
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              While we make every effort to display accurate pricing, features, and specs for listed tools, third-party software pricing packages change frequently. Imperial Picks does not guarantee the absolute accuracy or current relevance of pricing lists. If you spot discrepancies, please let us know so we can fix them.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 6 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              6. Third-Party Links
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              We contain outbound links directing you to third-party tools and websites. Imperial Picks does not review, verify, or endorse the content, safety, or stability of these external resources, nor do we accept responsibility for any transactions you conduct on those platforms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Section 7 -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2 mb-4">
              7. Governing Law
            </h2>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              These Terms & Conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with local legal frameworks, without regard to conflict of law principles. Any dispute arising from these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the competent courts.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact Details -->
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-100">
            <h3 class="font-display text-base font-bold text-slate-900">Legal Contact</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              For legal notifications, copyright claims, or terms inquiries, please contact our legal desk at:
              <a href="mailto:imperialpicks00@gmail.com" class="text-indigo-600 font-bold hover:underline ml-1">
                imperialpicks00@gmail.com
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
